{"tid":1881951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我要求咁低都搵唔到工做，壓力大到日日想死","createTime":"2020-02-16T01:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T08:13:00.000Z","uid":236500,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0636c9fd5fe0aba1bbe7f9fb8d2064ec56d96412","tid":1881951,"uid":236500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"我上年4月辭職，一直搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明有時見工都幾順利，但一直冇offer<br />\n已經由想搵夢想職業，改搵個一行就得，再改搵埋周邊行業同其他19工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我對果行有熱情，有知識，又勤力，只係畢業左1，2年，冇經驗<br />\n點解！點解！點解！<br />\n<br />\n搵左甘耐，得份19補習杜比offer我，完全唔係我果行，我又好討厭D壞細路，只係我有教細路經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知依家1個武漢肺炎攪到停課，連19補習社都叫我唔好返住，之後可能都凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家日日好大壓力，覺得自己好失敗，唔明點解咁耐都搵唔到工。自己本身又咩都冇，A0,冇錢，冇工，冇運氣，冇將來，日日好想死，好想跳樓，一係就返轉大陸再去報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd0b0979b5151e77afab13fa2c10744ebdd0ec4","tid":1881951,"uid":270166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T01:34:23.000Z","msg":"樓主本身做邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c008568be7150332ff980c5d0e9ca7421e1595","tid":1881951,"uid":21911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco